":83692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:05:57.000Z","msg":"點解同我情況咁似...<br />\n隨住年紀愈大啲意見分岐愈多<br />\n我自己呢啲&ldquo;聲音&rdquo;通常係base on朋友/屋企人"},{"pid":"ef837deac7d3c0136c2d064d331b8324726b7d46","tid":413562,"uid":149210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:07:34.000Z","msg":"樓主真心問我真心答<br />\n我都有類似情況但係唔係經常<br />\n但係另一個自己好躁狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933768ad788a7cee7d06061d0c56426346f12f1c","tid":413562,"uid":138606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:08:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>See doctor</blockquote><br />\n其實係想睇下有冇巴絲都有同我同樣既情況<br />\n一齊生活左咁耐都冇乜野 仲幾幫到手 應該暫時唔會打算睇醫生了<br />\n除非佢突然暴走 搞到我行為失常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e30eb39972779eb1b3ee164edf71259756db24","tid":413562,"uid":138606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:08:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解同我情況咁似...<br />\n隨住年紀愈大啲意見分岐愈多<br />\n我自己呢啲&ldquo;聲音&rdquo;通常係base on朋友/屋企人</blockquote><br />\n我果把完全係自己把聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba8ab73df259e44aaaa18bfa0a548f374185aa5","tid":413562,"uid":138606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:09:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主真心問我真心答<br />\n我都有類似情況但係唔係經常<br />\n但係另一個自己好躁狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁巴打佢有影響到你既日常生活嗎？"},{"pid":"d80d8811f1490a2d85b599dcd0d5d1537a21eba8","tid":413562,"uid":138606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:12:03.000Z","msg":"毒撚開po冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751523fc8a4b83b1099334957fd63f333d881b8d","tid":413562,"uid":149210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:19:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主真心問我真心答<br />\n我都有類似情況但係唔係經常<br />\n但係另一個自己好躁狂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出現了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁巴打佢有影響到你既日常生活嗎？</blockquote><br />\n咁又冇喎<br />\n平時出街自己都會好節制好留意自己行為<br />\n屋企就等屋企人走哂或者返房先由佢慢慢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時會心情好好但係突然會去攞支筆扮拎住把刀 牙磨下磨下咁扮黑社會劈友咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩<span style=\"font-size: small;\">應該</span>咁大個仔都無人發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11bf20a8b027d5224a2aeb1f315b0b981509e6b5","tid":413562,"uid":149210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:20:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒撚開po冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4db1bb1a63c7d86d8102d38a1d0814ebf3406b71","tid":413562,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:21:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>See doctor</blockquote><br />\n其實係想睇下有冇巴絲都有同我同樣既情況<br />\n一齊生活左咁耐都冇乜野 仲幾幫到手 應該暫時唔會打算睇醫生了<br />\n除非佢突然暴走 搞到我行為失常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n傻既，你又知邊個係真係既你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你覺你係你點知你先係真正既你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a30888765b459d227be440f1e8bcaf4afee5bd","tid":413562,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:22:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過呢種應該係 思覺失調</blockquote><br />\n假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實呢種算唔算係人類可以進化既路徑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/face